com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.data

Class WZDataMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.data.WZDataMap

  • public class WZDataMap
extends Object
    A key-based collection of WZDataItem elements that can be used as...
    • the set of named parameters for a WZDataEvent instance
    • a set of metadata added to a broadcast stream using WZStreamConfig.setStreamMetadata(WZDataMap)
    • a set of query string parameters for the connection url specified via WZStreamConfig.setConnectionParameters(WZDataMap)
